metadata.name: COFFEE AND CIGARETTES
metadata.description:
My last mint process for 2022. 
A new chapter of Photography begins in 2023 (hopefully) so this is the best way to salute this year. 

Collect now and burn it later. 
----  
There are going to be 5 NFTs (A-B-C-D-E).  
A & B will be open minted for free.  
To obtain C you will need to burn A + B  
To obtain D you will need to burn A + B + C  
To obtain E you will need to burn A + B + C + D  
If you want to have them all, I guess you should mint more copies :)  
Happy minting!
